name: Dawn Video Poker 3.5
overview: A really polished and well done video poker game created by Dawnbringer aka Richard Fhager and released as freeware in 2004. It was created using the AMOS development environment. An improvement on the original Dawn Video Poker and Dawn Video Poker 2.0 and 3.0 version, and it would be the final known version of the game created.
